  "texts": [
    "This is gradually leading organizations to assess the risks of their AI deployments based on risk management frameworks such as the NIST framework (NIST, 2021).",
    "In recent years, framework for AI risk assessment have also emerged such as the ISO/IEC 23894:2023 standard (ISO/IEC, 2023).",
    "The latter helps organizations to integrate risk management in their AI-related activities.",
    "At the regulatory forefront, the AI Act is also adopting a risk-driven approach to the regulatory compliance of AI deployment.",
    "Specifically, according to the AI Act, policymakers that use ML for data-driven policy development must perform a risk assessment of their AI systems."
  ],
